  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Half Price ski hire or carriage - Winter 2020/21 Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>This offer is subject to availability and may be withdrawn at any time.</li>
<li>Offer applicable to new bookings only made from 17<sup>th</sup> December 2019 – “while stocks last”.</li>
<li>Offer applies to Inghams ski and Ski Total bookings</li>
<li>All dates 19/20 and 20/21 departures – no restrictions</li>
<li>Available for ski holidays to France, Austria, Switzerland, Italy, and Slovenia - not available in Japan and Canada.</li>
<li>Lift pass and ski hire/carriage must be added to booking at least six weeks before departure date.</li>
<li>The offer is based on skis/boards/boots or carriage of skis only and not on special packages such as Learn to Ski and Ski Inclusive. </li>
<li>The discount received will vary depending on which ski pack is booked. See individual resort pages.</li>
<li>Lift pass and ski equipment is provided for 6 days.</li>
<li>Half price ski carriage only available on charter flights - please ask at time of booking.</li>
<li>*£129 per person saving for Grindelwald, Switzerland.</li>
</ul>
<p>Holidays are bound by Inghams' full <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms &amp; conditions</a>.</p>]]></bodyText>
